" dir="ltr" data-animation=""><div class="swiper-wrapper elementor-slides"><div class="elementor-repeater-item-a3d69b6 swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="Lufkin-Facality outside"></div><div class="elementor-background-overlay"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">Walk in clinic in Lufkin, TX</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">Walk in clinic near Lufkin, TX. Walk in any time. You get a room fast. Our on-site CT, X-rays, and lab help diagnose strokes, fractures, infections, and heart concerns in one visit.</div><a href="tel:9364271313" target="_blank" class="elementor-button elementor-slide-button elementor-size-sm">Call Our Pediatric Team</a></div></div></div><div class="elementor-repeater-item-37e1f23 swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="Exterior of ER of Lufkin 24/7 emergency room in Lufkin TX"></div><div class="elementor-background-overlay"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading"> In Lufkin Texas you'll get Hospitals level treatment.</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">In Emergency Room Lufkin TX, No waiting for answers. Our on-site CT scans, pharmacy, X-rays, and lab testing diagnose strokes, fractures, infections, and heart conditions all under one roof. In Lufkin Texas you'll get Hospitals level treatment.</div><a href="/about" class="elementor-button elementor-slide-button elementor-size-sm"> Learn About Our Technology</a></div></div></div><div class="elementor-repeater-item-c6f0057 swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="ER of Lufkin Facility"></div><div class="elementor-background-overlay"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">Emergency Room Lufkin TX</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">When an emergency strikes, you don't need another reason to worry. At ER of Lufkin, we are dedicated to providing immediate, expert medical care for you and your family. Our doors are open 24/7, and our board-certified physicians are here to provide the highest level of care without the long waits of a traditional hospital. We believe in transparency, communication, and a patient-first approach.</div><a href="/services" target="_blank" class="elementor-button elementor-slide-button elementor-size-sm">View Our Services</a></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-swiper-button elementor-swiper-button-prev" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Previous slide"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-eicon-chevron-left" viewBox="0 0 1000 1000" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M646 125C629 125 613 133 604 142L308 442C296 454 292 471 292 487 292 504 296 521 308 533L604 854C617 867 629 875 646 875 663 875 679 871 692 858 704 846 713 829 713 812 713 796 708 779 692 767L438 487 692 225C700 217 708 204 708 187 708 171 704 154 692 142 675 129 663 125 646 125Z"></path></svg></div><div class="elementor-swiper-button elementor-swiper-button-next" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Next slide"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-eicon-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 1000 1000" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M696 533C708 521 713 504 713 487 713 471 708 454 696 446L400 146C388 133 375 125 354 125 338 125 325 129 313 142 300 154 292 171 292 187 292 204 296 221 308 233L563 492 304 771C292 783 288 800 288 817 288 833 296 850 308 863 321 871 338 875 354 875 371 875 388 867 400 854L696 533Z"></path></svg></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9345299 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="9345299" data-element_type="container"><div class="e-con-inner"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-581fd46 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="581fd46" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b62b94f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="b62b94f" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://jayard.sg-host.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Emergency Room Lufkin TX</a></h1></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-77b3a1a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="77b3a1a" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>Emergency Room Lufkin TX is open around the clock. That is the simple promise. You can walk in any time and see a medical team that treats emergencies for adults and children. Results come back fast because imaging and lab testing happen here, on site.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ee42cdb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ee42cdb" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>ER of Lufkin provides immediate emergency care in Lufkin, TX. Our board-certified ER physicians and experienced nurses are on site 24/7. You get expert treatment with a minimum wait.</p><ul><li><strong>24/7 Emergency Care</strong></li><li><strong>Fast Triage &amp; No Long Waits</strong></li><li><strong>Advanced Diagnostics</strong></li><li><strong>Comprehensive Care for All Ages</strong> </li><li><strong>Compassionate &amp; Comfortable Environment</strong></li></ul><p>ER of Lufkin is here for you 365 days a year, because emergencies do not wait and neither should you.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7dbcf94 elementor-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="7dbcf94" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/KmZN87wJ6aei9vKm8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">Get Direction</span> </span> </a></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5dfa19e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="5dfa19e" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-31e933b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="31e933b" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"> <img decoding="async" width="1080" height="1080" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-6458 lazyload" alt="ER-near-lufkin-tx" data-srcset="https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx.jpeg 1080w, https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx-1024x1024.jpeg 1024w, https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx-768x768.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" title="Home Page – ER of Lufkin 1 Home Page – ER of Lufkin"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1080" height="1080" src="https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-6458 lazyload" alt="ER-near-lufkin-tx" srcset="https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx.jpeg 1080w, https://eroflufkin.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ER-near-lufkin-tx-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://er