id="ca43411" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="spacer.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-spacer"><div class="elementor-spacer-inner"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-24b2f4f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="24b2f4f" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="e-con-inner"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-dab0404 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="dab0404" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-09654a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="09654a6" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">When to Visit ER of Lufkin?</h2></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0d22648 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="0d22648" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-divider"> <span class="elementor-divider-separator"> </span></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-391a505 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="391a505" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>Seek immediate care for: </p><p>• Severe burns or head trauma<br data-start="1729" data-end="1732" />• Chest pain or irregular heartbeat<br data-start="1767" data-end="1770" />• Sudden confusion or slurred speech<br data-start="1806" data-end="1809" />• Uncontrolled bleeding<br data-start="1832" data-end="1835" />• High fever in infants or children<br data-start="1870" data-end="1873" />• Severe shortness of breath<br data-start="1901" data-end="1904" />• Dehydration with vomiting</p></div></div><di